sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    browser->>browser: User writes a note and clicks save button

    browser->>browser: Client-side validation

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: 200 Success
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: Updated notes via JSON
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: The browser updates the page with the new note